  "title": "Quantity Surveyor",
  "description": "<ul><li>Liaise with Client and Consultants on all contractual issues.</li><li>Preparation of tender & quotation submission and follow up with tender clarifications and interview.</li><li>Responsible for quantity take off and cost estimation</li><li>Preparation and resolution of progress claims, variation orders and final accounts.</li><li>Evaluation and certification of subcontractors’ progress claims, variation orders and final account.</li><li>Source quotation, liaise and negotiate with subcontractors and suppliers</li><li>Attend site meetings to capture all variation claims, preparation of interim valuations and potential variation works</li><li>Handle other assigned duties or related job as required</li></ul><p>Interested applicants, please apply online or send your resume in WORD format to <strong>davidnhbsg@gmail.com; ram@deshingroup.com; wayne@deshinhroup.com; shawn@deshingroup.com</strong></p><p>Thank you for your application but we regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>",
